entry.title: Azure/azure-dev
entry.summary: A developer CLI that accelerates the time it takes for you to get started on Azure. The Azure Developer CLI (azd) provides a set of developer-friendly commands that map to key stages in your workflow - code, build, deploy, monitor, repeat.
